1. Run Python Script

cd ~/Documents/Arducam/ArduCam_EVK_Demo/python
python project/sync.py -c ~/Documents/Arducam/Config/4000x3000_12fps_clear2.cfg

Convert Raw to video:
ffmpeg \
-f rawvideo \
-pix_fmt bayer_gbrg8\
-video_size 4000x3000 \
-framerate 10 \
-i recording_2026-02-28_12-06-08.raw \
output_2.mp4


Faster Conversion:
ffmpeg \
-f rawvideo \
-pix_fmt bayer_gbrg8 \
-video_size 4000x3000 \
-framerate 10 \
-i recording.raw \
-preset ultrafast \
-crf 28 \
output.mp4
